title: Modern 2 Bedroom Available NOW On Redmonds Marymoor Park!

posting_body: ['This is a 976sqft 2x2.', 'Live on the Park.', ' Urban comforts, outdoor living right.', 'Wander trails along the waterfront.', 'Wrap yourself in luxury.', 'Wake up every day to the wild-hearted beauty of the Pacific Northwest – it’s right outside your window at Bell Marymoor Park.', 'From our free-spirited rooftop deck to the light-filled arboretum, every element is designed to enhance your indoor/outdoor lifestyle.', 'Roam far in your own backyard when you live next door to Marymoor Park, an immense green playground for recreation and relaxation.', 'We’re directly on the bike trail and just a few minutes away from Downtown Redmond and East Lake Sammamish.', '-24-hour fitness studio', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Clubhouse', '-Tide laundry lockers', '-In-Unit Laundry', '-High Ceilings in all First Floor Homes', '-640 acres of outdoor recreation possibilities at your doorstep', '-Side-by-side Refrigerators with Ice Makers', '-Wood Plank Inspired Flooring', '-Close proximity to burke-gilman trail', '-Reading coves throughout community', '-Dishwasher', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing and Specials subject to change daily and restrictions may apply.', 'Please contact leasing agent for details.', 'Pricing and specials change daily.', 'Please inquire via our website at <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity Statement: We are pledged to the letter and spirit of U.S. policy for the achievement of equal housing opportunity throughout the Nation.', 'We encourage and support an affirmative advertising and marketing program in which there are no barriers to obtaining housing because of race, color, religion, sex, handicap, familial status, or national origin.']
